                "children": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Scribe's Insight."
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " You know the "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Message"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " cantrip. You can also cast the "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Comprehend Languages"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " spell with this trait. Starting at 3rd level, you can also cast the "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Magic Mouth"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " spell with it. Once you cast either spell with this trait, you can't cast that spell again until you finish a Long Rest. Intelligence is your Spellcasting Ability for these spells."
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      },
